    "awaitingMac.subtitle": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "اترك هذه الشاشة مفتوحة. على Mac، أكمل الإعداد حتى يقول Soyeht \"Waiting for your iPhone.\""
          }
        },
        "bn": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "এই স্ক্রিনটি খোলা রাখুন। আপনার Mac-এ, Soyeht \"Waiting for your iPhone.\" বলা পর্যন্ত সেটআপ শেষ করুন।"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lassen Sie diesen Bildschirm geöffnet. Schließen Sie auf Ihrem Mac die Einrichtung ab, bis Soyeht \"Waiting for your iPhone.\" anzeigt."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Keep this screen open. On your Mac, finish setup until Soyeht says \"Waiting for your iPhone.\""
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mantén esta pantalla abierta. En tu Mac, termina la configuración hasta que Soyeht diga \"Waiting for your iPhone.\""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gardez cet écran ouvert. Sur votre Mac, terminez la configuration jusqu’à ce que Soyeht affiche \"Waiting for your iPhone.\""
          }
        },
        "hi": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "इस screen को खुला रखें। अपने Mac पर setup पूरा करें जब तक Soyeht \"Waiting for your iPhone.\" न कहे।"
          }
        },
        "id": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Biarkan layar ini terbuka. Di Mac Anda, selesaikan penyiapan sampai Soyeht menampilkan \"Waiting for your iPhone.\""
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "この画面を開いたままにしてください。Mac で Soyeht が \"Waiting for your iPhone.\" と表示するまで設定を進めます。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "이 화면을 열어 두세요. Mac에서 Soyeht이 \"Waiting for your iPhone.\"이라고 표시할 때까지 설정을 완료하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "保持此屏幕打开。在 Mac 上完成设置，直到 Soyeht 显示“Waiting for your iPhone.”"
          }
        },
        "mr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ही screen उघडी ठेवा. तुमच्या Mac वर Soyeht \"Waiting for your iPhone.\" म्हणेपर्यंत setup पूर्ण करा."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mantenha esta tela aberta. No Mac, termine a configuração até o Soyeht dizer \"Waiting for your iPhone.\""
          }
        },
        "pt-PT": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mantenha este ecrã aberto. No Mac, termine a configuração até o Soyeht dizer \"Waiting for your iPhone.\""
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Оставьте этот экран открытым. На Mac завершите настройку, пока Soyeht не покажет \"Waiting for your iPhone.\""
          }
        },
        "te": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ఈ screen తెరిచి ఉంచండి. మీ Mac లో Soyeht \"Waiting for your iPhone.\" అని చెప్పే వరకు setup పూర్తి చేయండి."
          }
        },
        "ur": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "یہ screen کھلی رکھیں۔ اپنے Mac پر setup مکمل کریں جب تک Soyeht \"Waiting for your iPhone.\" نہ کہے۔"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Awaiting Mac subtitle instructing the user to finish setup on Mac while the iPhone waits."
    },
